{
  "title": "Wcharred Dense Yakimono-Grilled Beef Scallop Shell Wraps",
  "description": "A flexitarian-friendly meal-prep Russian dish featuring charred dense yakimono-grilled beef wrapped in a sesame seed oil-infused scallop shell. Perfect for busy weekdays.",
