  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high.",
    "Mix yakimono-grill oil with sesame seed paste, salt, and squeeze of lemon juice. Rub mixture onto beef slices.",
    "Grill beef slices for 3 minutes on each side until charred, then set aside.",
    "Clean scallop shells under cold water and pat dry.",
    "Spread a thin layer of sesame seed paste over the inside of each scallop shell.",
    "Place grilled beef slices in centers of scallop shells. Drizzle with rice vinegar and soy sauce mixture.",
    "Top with sesame seeds and serve."
